debrief.itemText: Please answer the following questions about your experience. Click and drag the red scrollbar to move down. Do not leave any box blank. Type ‘no’ or ‘n/a’ if you don’t have a response.
Briefly describe what you were asked to do in this experiment? (if there is existing text in the box delete it.
debrief.response: The first part asked me to choose between two shapes for point value purposes, the cecond asked me to choose whether a number was above or betow 153, the third part had me choose whether a letter was closer to A or Z, and the last two sections had me choose between answering the letter or number question. The second one of these had a point value system associated with it and had 8 blocks.

debrief.itemText: Was there any part of the experiment that you found to be confusing?
Please explain anything you found confusing. (if No, type ‘No’)
How hard did you try during the experiment?
To what degree was your behavior influenced by the colored shapes?
Do you have any final comments on the experiment? (If no, just type No)
debrief.response: The Respond Faster!" was quite annoying
debrief.rt: especially when I tried to answer a question to the best of my ability and recieved no points."
